issue.title: Visual bell animation on Mac is really long
issue.body:
On macOS, the visual bell animation lasts for around 1 second regardless of what non-zero duration is in the config file. This seems to be the case since commit 80d4daccc307622f8e604af4f36ac89ecccf5db7.

Before that commit, visual bell animation worked fine.

pull_request.title: Fix clippy warnings
pull_request.body:
Tested in 8 combinations:
```
cargo {+stable,+nightly} clippy {,--all-targets} {,--release}
```

Fixed warnings about unused imports. One import is only used for tests, another import is not needed at all.

Fixed clippy warning about `skip(0)` by using a constant variable. It started affecting stable Rust, the warning is detected on Rust 1.73.

Replaced `get(0)` with `first()` in tests as suggested by nightly clippy.

pull_request.title: Avoid maximizing window when creating new tab
pull_request.body:
This patch clears the startup mode when creating a new tab on macOS to avoid maximizing an existing window.

Fixes #7313
